    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 4. Validation results demonstrate RH < 1.0 at all five operating points using the analyst-chosen configuration settings (mesh 3.8M cells, y+ = 1, alpha = 1.0). The assessment team notes that configuration parameters are documented in the validation report narrative but acknowledges that no formal configuration-binding mechanism has been implemented to constrain deployment-time parameter selection. This gap is considered acceptable given that the simulation protocol SOP references the validation report; however, no automated enforcement prevents deviation from the validated parameter set at deployment.",
